@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Learning Center";
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>

<p>This virtual "Learning Center" is a demo of a multi-layer architectured MVC website utilizing SQL database, for the final project of University of Washington, CSHP-230 class by Roham Pardakhtim. </p>
<p>Below is a snapshot of this project's architecture:</p>
<img src="~/Content/Architecture.jpg" height="200"/>
<p>The purpose of this multi layer architecture is to isolate the raw data from the database, from the UI logic as much as possible for the sake of secutiry, reliability, ease of maintenance, troubleshooting, improvement, and etc. </p>
<p></p>
<h2>Some features of this project are:</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Ability to register a new unique user.</li>
    <li>Ability for users to Log in/Log off.</li>
    <li>Page to: Display a list of available classes.</li>
    <li>Page to: Display a list of classes for a user to register (log in required).</li>
    <li>Page to: Display a list of classes a user is registered for (log in required).</li>
</ul>

